A Studio Ghibli style illustration of an intimate vegetarian restaurant scene in Melbourne at dusk, warm golden light spilling from paper lanterns onto a rustic wooden table laden with colorful, artfully arranged plant-based dishes—vibrant greens, orange carrots, purple cabbage, edible flowers scattered across ceramic plates. Steam rises gently from bowls, creating a dreamy atmosphere. Through the window, the silhouette of Melbourne's Fitzroy neighborhood with Victorian-era buildings. A curious cat sits on a windowsill watching the scene. Rich earthy tones of moss green, terracotta, and warm amber dominate the palette, with soft watercolor textures and the characteristic whimsical, cozy feeling of animated Japanese films.
